1. pip3 install flask
2. pip3 install captcha
3. python3 -m flask run
4. python3 app.py # Alternative method
5. ./Multich.sh # Alternative method 

# Basic info
Script runs by default at 127.0.0.1 port 5000. Using nginx or lighttpd,
it's fairly simple to point a domain name and port 80 or 443 at the
server.

Modify settings.py setting "name" to set the name of your board;
add boards you want to link with in the "friends" part of the configuration.

Moderation tool to come that does the following:
* blacklist certain terms
* delete thread / post 
* delete all posts by IP
* ban IP address
* ban IP range

# Directory structure
```
in ./threads/ :

./site/threads/######/head
	title \n tag
	
./site/threads/######/local
./site/threads/######/sitename
	time<>name<>comment
	
./site/threads/######/list
	shortname time

./site/list
	optime lastreply localreplies allreplies title

./site/tags
	tagname optime optime optime
./list
	board optime lastreply localreplies allreplies title

./tags
	tagname board-optime board-optime

./friends
	shortname url
	shortname url
	shortname url


```